<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Innovative Agricultural Solutions</title>
    <style>
        /* General Reset */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        /* Ensure the page takes full height */
        html, body {
            height: 100%;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #a1c4fd, #c2e9fb);
            color: #333;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        body {
            padding: 2rem;
            flex: 1; /* This ensures that the body content expands */
        }

        header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }

        header p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #34495e;
        }

        section {
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        section h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }

        section p {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .highlight {
            color: #1e90ff;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            color: #34495e;
            padding: 1rem;
            background-color: #f1f1f1;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Innovative Agricultural Solutions</h1>
        <p>Empowering People to Control Their Agricultural Lands Remotely</p>
    </header>

    <section>
        <h2>1. Smart Irrigation System</h2>
        <p>
            Our innovative <span class="highlight">Smart Irrigation System</span> uses advanced IoT sensors to monitor soil moisture levels in real-time. 
            By integrating with a <span class="highlight">Weather API</span>, we can predict rain and adjust irrigation schedules automatically. 
            This ensures optimal water usage, prevents overwatering, and helps maintain healthy crop growth.
        </p>
        <p>
            Benefits:
            <ul>
                <li>Conserves water by up to 50% compared to traditional methods.</li>
                <li>Prevents crop diseases caused by overwatering.</li>
                <li>Increases yield and reduces manual labor.</li>
            </ul>
        </p>
        <p>
            Our system also provides real-time alerts and reports through the website, enabling remote control and monitoring.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>2. Smart IoT Surveillance Cameras</h2>
        <p>
            The <span class="highlight">Smart Surveillance System</span> includes IoT-enabled CC cameras that provide 24/7 live feeds accessible from our website. 
            These cameras are powered by <span class="highlight">solar energy</span>, ensuring sustainable and uninterrupted operation.
        </p>
        <p>
            Features:
            <ul>
                <li>Voice-controlled operation for easy access and management.</li>
                <li>Fully waterproof, ensuring durability in harsh weather conditions.</li>
                <li>Real-time motion detection and alerts sent directly to your device.</li>
            </ul>
        </p>
        <p>
            This solution is designed to enhance security, allowing you to monitor your agricultural land from anywhere in the world.
        </p>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Farners Hub</p>
    </footer>
</body>

</html>
